Class MAEFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • OutputFileFormat
      • MAEFile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FileFormat

    public class MAEFile
extends OutputFileFormat
    Parses Macromodel geometry files. It's expected a full block and partial blocks will be present. I'm not bothering to read the atoms or any other data.
